query.pigql: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "true" ; hasArticle = filter q by 'ArticleVersion' > 0; c = group hasArticle by all, q by all; c = foreach c generate count(hasArticle)/count(q) as 'avg_AttachedRate';

q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by IsClosed=="true";hasArticle = filter q by 'ArticleVersion' > 0; hasArticle = group hasArticle by all; hasArticle = foreach hasArticle generate "With Articles" as 'Cases',  avg('DurationCalculatedField') as 'avg_CaseDuration'; noArticle = filter q by 'ArticleVersion' == 0; noArticle = group noArticle by all; noArticle = foreach noArticle generate "Without Articles" as 'Cases',  avg('DurationCalculatedField') as 'avg_CaseDuration'; u = group hasArticle by all, noArticle by all; u = foreach u generate -(sum(hasArticle['avg_CaseDuration'])-sum(noArticle['avg_CaseDuration']))/sum(noArticle['avg_CaseDuration'])*100 as 'avg_Percent';

q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'IsClosed' == "true" ;  hasArticle = filter q by 'ArticleVersion' > 0; c = group hasArticle by 'Product_Family_KB__c', q by 'Product_Family_KB__c'; c = foreach c generate count(hasArticle)/count(q) as 'avg_AttachedRate', hasArticle['Product_Family_KB__c'] as 'Product_Family_KB__c'; c = order c by 'avg_AttachedRate' {{cell(static_1.selection, 0, "value").asString()}};

step_ValuesTable.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by {{cell(Toggle_AttachedArticles.selection, 0, "saql").asObject()}}; q = foreach q generate 'CaseNumber', first('Account_Name') as 'Account_Name', first('CSAT__c') as 'CSAT__c', first('First_Contact_Close__c') as 'First_Contact_Close__c', first('Type') as 'Type', first('Owner_Name') as 'Owner_Name', first('MilestoneStatus__c') as 'MilestoneStatus__c', avg('Time_Open__c') as 'avg_Time_Open__c', first('Origin') as 'Origin', first('Priority') as 'Priority', first('Status') as 'Status',   first('Type_of_Support__c') as 'Type_of_Support__c', first('IsEscalated') as 'Escalated'; q = limit q 100;

query.pigql: q = load "${App.Datasets.ServiceCase_tp.FullyQualifiedName}";q = filter q by IsClosed=="true"; q = filter q by 'CSAT' > -10; hasArticle = filter q by 'ArticleVersion' > 0; hasArticle = group hasArticle by all; hasArticle = foreach hasArticle generate "With Articles" as 'Cases',  avg('CSAT') as 'avg_CSAT'; noArticle = filter q by 'ArticleVersion' == 0; noArticle = group noArticle by all; noArticle = foreach noArticle generate "Without Articles" as 'Cases',  avg('CSAT') as 'avg_CSAT'; u = group hasArticle by all, noArticle by all; u = foreach u generate (sum(hasArticle['avg_CSAT'])-sum(noArticle['avg_CSAT']))/sum(noArticle['avg_CSAT'])*100 as 'avg_Percent';
